flowchart LR
  U[Founder input] --> Q[Qwen Cloud Agent Orchestrator]
  Q --> S[Workflow State Store]
  Q --> T[Tool Adapters]
  T --> P[Proof and Verification Results]
  P --> A[Artifact Generator]
  S --> A
  A --> H[Human Review Console]
  H --> G{Approval Gate}
  G -->|approved| X[External Action Adapter]
  G -->|not approved| B[Blocked or Draft State]
  X --> L[Action Logger]
  B --> L
  L --> S
  Q -. policy checks .-> G
  D[Alibaba Cloud Deployment] --> Q
  D --> UI[Public Demo UI]
  UI --> U
